{"tid":2463730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉淑儀感激國台辦點名稱讚　形容是「無意的收獲」 但拒絕銷毀外國產品","createTime":"2021-03-27T02:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T03:30:56.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd17e5f131367bf0edbb1f009a597029790fc6d","tid":2463730,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"日前被國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮點名稱讚，指她在一場外媒主辦的研討會上，離場抗議有與會者指「台灣是國家」，是表達正義之聲，作出有力批駁。葉劉淑儀表示，感激國台辦的讚揚，形容是無意的收獲，說答應出席研討會前，不知道同場有「台獨份子」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又表示，已決定停買及停用牽涉「新疆棉風波」的品牌產品，但不認為需要採取進一步行動，包括銷毀現有產品。"},{"pid":"a79d1ebe4b2cafdca6fbdfb97b314a26125072cf","tid":2463730,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"個女繼續留係英國效忠英女王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://myblogs.asia/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Image-2021-02-11-at-10.13.08-PM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-02-11-at-10.13.08-PM.jpeg&h=0a39aaba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"864c722f436092c87fde34f27a1543ce23796e71","tid":2463730,"uid":373119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"停經老女人你唔係仲諗住有得上位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210e6e5fa8c3a9c9d3dfb22c306adef67c7e06e0","tid":2463730,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"身體最誠實"},{"pid":"4649bb438a7583d0d0a2925ce7b7615ea3bff01d","tid":2463730,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"忠誠的狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12315470daf5f1976706fab07b52863bca8dfb40","tid":2463730,"uid":325869,"like":0,"disli